 </disp-formula>The same analysis for all 8 isolated crystals yielded an average BrQ coverage of around 0.070 ± 0.035, that is, 7 ± 3.5%. Further experiments with a higher spatial resolution are required to determine the different affinities of BrQ to the {100} and the {010} faces of hemozoin (
 <xref rid="r8" ref-type="bibr">8</xref>).
